= editor of the CyberUnions blog

=Bio=

"My name is Walton Pantland. I am a trade union official based in Glasgow, Scotland, where I work for Unite, the biggest union in the UK. This website is a personal exploration of the impact new technologies can have on union organising. It contains both boring theoretical pieces (sorry), and more practical resources for activists."
(http://cyberunions.org/about/)

